flowchart TD
    subgraph Registro
        A[Peso kg] --> D[POST /weight]
        B[Agua ml] --> E[POST /hydration]
        C[Humor 1-5] --> F[POST /mood]
    end

    D & E & F --> G[(PostgreSQL)]

    G --> H[Graficos no dashboard]
    G --> I[Insights e relatorios IA]
    G --> J[Lembretes de hidratacao]
    G --> K[Recalculo mensal TDEE]
